highlights.text: “Vết Mưa” by Vũ Cát Tường is the biggest gainer on Top Songs Vietnam, up 96 spots at #76.
EM XINH "SAY HI" has the most spots on Top Songs Vietnam. “NGƯỜI ĐẦU TIÊN” is the highest at #2.
“Âm Thầm Bên Em” by Sơn Tùng M-TP has been on Top Songs Vietnam the longest, at 1719 days straight.
